# Tier:      STANDARD
# SEVERITY DISCREPANCY: NVD/vulnx says 7.2 (HIGH) — CVE.org (CNA, v4.0) says 6 (MEDIUM). See https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2026-0286
# Generated: 2026-07-14T20:48:02.158105Z
